snippet.title: Post Malone, Swae Lee - Sunflower (Spider-Man: Into the Spider-Verse) (Official Video)
snippet.description:
"Sunflower" is the #1 hit-single from the official soundtrack album Spider-Man™: Into the Spider-Verse. Get the song here: https://postmalone.lnk.to/sunflowerYD 

The single re-teams Post Malone & Swae Lee after the two joined forces for “Spoil My Night” from the year’s biggest multi-platinum album, beerbongs & bentleys.

Phil Lord and Christopher Miller, the creative minds behind The Lego Movie and 21 Jump Street, bring their unique talents to a fresh vision of a different Spider-Man Universe, with a groundbreaking visual style that’s the first of its kind. Spider-Man™: Into the Spider-Verse introduces Brooklyn teen Miles Morales, and the limitless possibilities of the Spider-Verse, where more than one can wear the mask.
